author: John Ousterhout
message:
Fix bug in grant mechanism
Wasn't checking to send new grants when deleting RPCs.
Also added "flag" sysctl with HOMA_FLAG_LOG_ACTIVE_RPCS option
to log active messages.
Also added homa_symbol_for_state function.
files_changed: homa.h, homa_impl.h, homa_incoming.c, homa_plumbing.c, homa_timer.c, homa_utils.c, notes.txt, unit/Makefile, unit/unit_homa_incoming.c

author: John Ousterhout
message:
Added workload support to cp_node.
Fixed bug: homa_message_out_reset must copy GSO info.
Fixed bug: msgout.next_offset wasn't updated properly by homa_xmit_data.
Eliminated msgout.next_offset (just look in the packet).
Removed pipeline_xmit option (tricky to support with next_offset
elimination, hasn't shown any performance benefit yet).
Replaced HOMA_MIN_CLIENT_PORT checks with is_client checks.
files_changed: cloudlab/bin/start_xl170, cloudlab/update, homa_impl.h, homa_incoming.c, homa_outgoing.c, homa_plumbing.c, homa_timer.c, homa_utils.c, man/homa.7, notes.txt, test/unit_homa_outgoing.c, test/utils.c, timetrace.c, util/Makefile, util/cp_node.cc, util/dist.cc, util/dist.h

author: John Ousterhout
message: Removed "type" parameter from homa_recv and homa_recvv\nAlso, renamed HOMA_MIN_CLIENT_PORT to HOMA_MIN_DEFAULT_PORT and\nfixed several bits of stale documentation.
files_changed: homa.h, homa_api.c, homa_plumbing.c, homa_socktab.c, homa_utils.c, man/homa.7, man/homa_recv.3, test/mock.c, test/unit_homa_plumbing.c, test/unit_homa_socktab.c, util/cp_node.cc, util/homa_test.cc, util/server.cc

author: John Ousterhout
message: homa_ioc_recv didn't free RPCs after errors w. HOMA_RECV_PARTIAL

author: John Ousterhout
message:
Added GRO policy HOMA_GRO_IDLE_NEW
(Fixed load-balancing problem with HOMA_GRO_IDLE, where if SoftIRQ
was slow to start up, GRO would keep assigning more batches of
packets to it, instead of switching to a different core)
files_changed: homa_impl.h, homa_incoming.c, homa_offload.c, homa_plumbing.c, homa_utils.c, man/homa.7, test/unit_homa_offload.c, timetrace.c
